About V3  V3 is a rewrite of v2 started in January of 2020. Compared to V2, it features improved performance, a new theming system, multi-window support, and much more. It is currently being built with your feedback and support. It is still in Beta stage so it is not ready for the production use, but feel free to test it and report any issues.
      Download V3 Beta  Portable version   No installation; no automatic updates; bookmark this page and manually download the latest update every week overwriting the existing files
   ClickOnce web Installer   Has automatic updates. Program is not signed so it will show as Unknown author and security risk, so click &#34;More Info&#34; and then &#34;Run Anyway&#34;
